<section id="Section520261">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>items</primary>
      <secondary>by class code</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>class codes</primary>
      <secondary>item details for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Items by Class Code</title>
  <para>To view Items by Class Code, select the "Items by Class Code" option.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/dspItemsByClassCode.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Items by Class Code</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When displaying Items by Class Code, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>All Class Codes</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display Items for all Class Codes.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify Class Code whose Items you want to display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Pattern</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a Class Code pattern to select a range of Class Codes.
        Refine your search using Regular Expressions.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Inactive Items</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to show Inactive Items in the display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Items</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists Items by Class Code, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
